Package: philworkbench
Title: Philosophy Research Workbench
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yusuke", "Matsui", email = "mail.to.matsui@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An integrated workbench for computational philosophy research.
    Provides a unified verb-based interface (phil_read, phil_explore, phil_compare,
    phil_plot, etc.) that orchestrates all layers of the Phil ecosystem. Includes
    an interactive Shiny dashboard, Quarto integration for reproducible research,
    and export to LaTeX/BibTeX.
